---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy — AAA Devs">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-24">
    <div class="mb-12 flex justify-center">
      <a href="/">
        <img src="/images/logo.svg" alt="AAA Devs" class="h-56 w-auto sm:h-72" />
      </a>
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-text-muted">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <div class="mt-12 space-y-8 text-text-muted">
      <section>
        <p>AAA Devs operates this website (aaadevs.com) as a studio showcase. This page explains what limited information we process when you visit it. Our products are operated on their own websites and have their own privacy policies — for example, troniti is governed by the policy at <a href="https://troniti.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover">troniti.com</a>.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>This site does not require an account and does not ask you to submit personal data. We use Google Analytics, which collects standard, aggregated usage data such as:</p>
        <ul class="mt-2 list-inside list-disc space-y-1">
          <li>Pages visited and time spent on the site</li>
          <li>Approximate location (country/region) and language</li>
          <li>Device, browser, and referral information</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">How We Use This Data</h2>
        <ul class="list-inside list-disc space-y-1">
          <li>To understand how visitors use the site</li>
          <li>To improve our content and presentation</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">We do not sell your data. We do not display advertising on this site.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Your Choices</h2>
        <p>You can block analytics by using browser privacy settings, an ad/tracker blocker, or Google's <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover">opt-out tools</a>.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this policy, contact us at <a href="mailto:ahmlvs@aaadevs.com" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover">ahmlvs@aaadevs.com</a>.</p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16">
      <a href="/" class="text-sm text-text-muted hover:text-text">&larr; Back to home</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
